---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Brad Bennett">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium mb-8">About</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-[--color-text] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Brad Bennett is a strategist, musician, and artist based in Sydney, Australia.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        By day, he leads growth, digital strategy and media at <a href="https://papermoose.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-[--color-accent]">Paper Moose</a>, a B-Corp creative agency. His writing on creativity, ethics, and effectiveness has appeared in AdNews, Mumbrella, WARC, and LBB.
      </p>

      <p>
        By night (and weekends), he makes noise. He's performed with avant-garde composers Glenn Branca and Rhys Chatham as part of their legendary guitar orchestras, and currently plays synthesizers in the Sydney drone/doom band <a href="https://thegreymen.bandcamp.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-[--color-accent]">The Grey Men</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Previous bands include Bling Kong (an 11-piece NYC rock band featuring 4 cheerleaders, 3 drummers, and a video ninja — covered in Time Out New York and SPIN Magazine) and Kilowatthours (Brooklyn indie rock, Temporary Residence Ltd).
      </p>

      <p>
        His visual work spans sound art, photography, and artist books. Recent projects include the Tlön Encyclopaedia artist book series, the Noise 1 / Reverie sound installation at Ellipsis Gallery, and FujiFilm Instax photography exhibited at Head On Photo Festival.
      </p>

      <p>
        He also builds custom motorcycles. His Moto Guzzi V7 cafe racer has been featured in Return of the Cafe Racers and Throttle Roll.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mt-12 mb-4">Elsewhere</h2>
      
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-[--color-text-muted]">
        <li>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/bradfordbennett" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-[--color-accent]">LinkedIn ↗</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://thegreymen.bandcamp.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-[--color-accent]">The Grey Men (Bandcamp) ↗</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mt-12 mb-4">Volunteer</h2>
      
      <p>
        <strong><a href="https://jiamini.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-[--color-accent]">Jiamini</a></strong> — Director of Finance since 2007. A charity providing educational resources to students in Southern Tanzania.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <strong>NSW State Emergency Service</strong> — Volunteer member, assisting with storm, flood, and community emergency response.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
